=\"n\">n</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">‚Ñï</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">fact</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">finrank</span> <span class=\"bp\">ùïú</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">euclidean_space</span> <span class=\"bp\">ùïú</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">fin</span> <span class=\"n\">n</span><span class=\"o\">))</span> <span class=\"bp\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">n</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span>\n<span class=\"n\">module.free.fact_finrank_pi_fin</span> <span class=\"bp\">ùïú</span> <span class=\"n\">n</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\">-- only in your file, it shouldn't be a global instance (we can discuss why)</span>\n<span class=\"kn\">local</span> <span class=\"kn\">attribute</span> <span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"kd\">instance</span><span class=\"o\">]</span> <span class=\"n\">fact_finrank_euclidean</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
